                    <span>Although somewhat brief, this translation of the Tao Te Ching is concise, not lacking.  It is a good complement to the Arthur Waley translation, and well worth reading.  Read, compare, and keep for the art.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A Thing of Value</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
