                    <span>How can one place value on something?  What is value?  The Tao Te Ching is an amazing view of the world.  More specifically the work of "Art" by Gia-Fu Feng and Jane English is for lack of a better word; poetry.  Of all the translations of the Tao Te Ching I have read or attempted to read this translation stands alone.  It is concise and it flows in ways that no other translation of this great work ever have or potentially ever will.
<br />
<br /></span>
                  
